title: Episode 140: Igor – Why You Should Only Approach Women During The Day
description:
Show Notes:
How Igor got his reputation as Ukraine’s best day hunter… (01:00)

The one thing you must due to develop immunity to approach anxiety… (02:00)

What to say if a woman tells you she is married or has a boyfriend… (03:15)
How to manage the contact info from women on your phone… (05:00)

Why daygame is so much better than night-game… (07:30)

Where to go to meet women during the day? Should you walk around, drive or use other modes of transport… (09:00)

A fun game you can play while approaching to start a conversation and approach indirectly… (10:00)
Does it help to use a car during daygame and what kind of car should it be?… (13:40)

Why it’s VITAL to be good at daygame… (14:30)

How to avoid looking like a pickup artist while daygaming… (15:30)

Say this to a woman wearing a backpack… (17:00)

What to do if you accidentally hit on a girl who is under-age… (18:30)
What if you’re scared to do daygame because of your job, cancel-culture, and the me–too movement? (21:00)

What if you’re not good looking, well built, or rich?… (22:30)

Does standup comedy or improv help you improve at daygame?… (24:00)

The magic formula for improving at daygame… (25:05)

How many women do you need to approach per day to get good?… (25:45)
Do you need to have a good Instagram to succeed?… (27:30)

How to improve your Instagram… (29:00)

An easy hack to creating Instagram posts that get female attention… (32:30)

What if you don’t have Instagram or you have very few photos?… (34:00)

Links:
Igor’s Instagram - Junior & The Beast

I'm Robbie Kramer 🎙Host of The Inner Confidence Podcast & Founder of Inner Confidence, Inc.

I lived an exhilarating single life filled with adventures and lessons, and ultimately achieved what I had always aspired to – finding an amazing, feminine, and loving wife. 

I believe my experiences provide a rare balance of wild freedom and committed love, equipping me with the insights to help you navigate the complexities of dating and relationships in today's world. Let me guide you to embrace your desires, improve your social prowess, and ultimately attract the partner who aligns with your highest aspirations.

You won’t find any fluffy, new-age, or cringy stuff here, just tested, proven and actionable advice that yields results.

Apply to join our exclusive Inner Confidence Community of ambitious men who are actively working together to achieve their goals faster   ► https://innerconfidence.com/community

You can email me at robbie@innerconfidence.com with any questions or comments.
